ichele.jpg\" alt=\"Michele Mancarella\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Michele Mancarella<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">Postdoc.<br\/><a href=\"mailto:michele.mancarella@unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">michele.mancarella@unimib.it<\/a><br\/><em>Cosmologist, cosmo-expext, cosmo-something, cosmo-whatever. Uses stats, machine learning, and theory to challenge Einstein\u2019s gravity. Curses in front of a python script, trains in a muay thai gym, cooks risotto.<\/em><\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/costantino_square.jpg\" alt=\"Costantino Pacilio\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Costantino Pacilio<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">Postdoc. <br\/><a href=\"mailto:costantino.pacilio@unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">costantino.pacilio@unimib.it<\/a><br\/><em>Black-hole spectroscoper, equation of stater, pizza purist, coffee obsessed. Using black holes and neutron stars to understand our Universe. Reading comic books to explore parallel worlds. Listening to Bob Dylan to refresh my emotions.\u00a0<\/em><\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/swetha-photo-web.jpg\" alt=\"Swetha Bhagwat\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Swetha Bhagwat<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">Postdoc 