ued by all questions we cannot answer.<\/em><\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/alice_lq-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Alice Spadaro\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Alice Spadaro<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">PhD student. <br\/><a href=\"mailto:a.spadaro3@campus.unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">a.spadaro3@campus.unimib.it<br\/><\/a><em>Glitch hunter, data miner, gravitational-wave lover. Cares for nature, addicted to adventure sports. Likes building fun stuff with Lego bricks and gets charged up with rock music. Curious to learn something new and explore the universe.\u00a0<\/em><\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/giulia_square-2.jpg\" alt=\"Giulia Fumagalli\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Giulia Fumagalli<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">PhD student. <br\/><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:g.fumagalli47@campus.unimib.it\" target=\"_blank\">g.fumagalli47@campus.unimib.it<\/a><br\/><em>Pulsar analyzer, outlier nightmare, eccentricity calculator<\/em>. <em>Likes gravitational waves, black holes, and cats. Specialized in cakes, cookies, and any sweet treats<\/em> <em>(by far the best chocolate brownie in town!). Long-distance runner to let off steam.\u00a0<\/em><\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__av